trans-unit.source: Specifies how the list changed.

Used by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs.ListChangedType%2A> property of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs> class to indicate the way an <xref:System.ComponentModel.IBindingList> object changes.
trans-unit.target: Används av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs.ListChangedType%2A>egenskapen för den <xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs>klassen för att ange hur ett <xref:System.ComponentModel.IBindingList>ändras.</xref:System.ComponentModel.IBindingList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs.ListChangedType%2A>

trans-unit.source: An item added to the list.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt som lagts till i listan.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs.NewIndex*> contains the index of the item that was added.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs.NewIndex*>innehåller indexet för det objekt som har lagts till.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ListChangedEventArgs.NewIndex*>
